# JobConnect - MERN Stack Job Portal

![JobConnect](https://img.shields.io/badge/MERN-Stack-blue) ![MongoDB](https://img.shields.io/badge/MongoDB-Atlas-green) ![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-17-blue) ![Node](https://img.shields.io/badge/Node.js-18-green) ![TailwindCSS](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tailwind-CSS-blue)

A full stack job portal web application built with the MERN stack as a Final Year Project. JobConnect allows recruiters to post jobs and manage applicants, while job seekers can search, filter, and apply for jobs with resume upload.

---

