## вњЁ Features

### For Job Seekers
- Register and login securely with JWT
- Browse and search all job listings
- Filter jobs by location, type and skills
- Apply to jobs with cover letter and resume (PDF)
- Track application status (Applied, Reviewed, Accepted, Rejected)
- Personal dashboard to manage applications

### For Recruiters
- Register and login as a recruiter
- Post new job listings
- Manage and delete job postings
- View all applicants for each job
- Update application status for each candidate
- View applicant resumes and skills

