## рџ“Ў API Endpoints

### Auth Routes
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|--------|----------|-------------|--------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Register new user | Public |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login user | Public |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user | Private |
| PUT | `/api/auth/profile` | Update profile | Private |

### Job Routes
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|--------|----------|-------------|--------|
| GET | `/api/jobs` | Get all jobs | Public |
| GET | `/api/jobs/:id` | Get job by ID | Public |
| POST | `/api/jobs` | Create new job | Recruiter |
| PUT | `/api/jobs/:id` | Update job | Recruiter |
| DELETE | `/api/jobs/:id` | Delete job | Recruiter |
| GET | `/api/jobs/recruiter/myjobs` | Get recruiter's jobs | Recruiter |

### Application Routes
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|--------|----------|-------------|--------|
| POST | `/api/applications/:jobId` | Apply to job | Job Seeker |
| GET | `/api/applications/my` | Get my applications | Job Seeker |
| GET | `/api/applications/job/:jobId` | Get job applications | Recruiter |
| PUT | `/api/applications/:id/status` | Update status | Recruiter |

